descriptionHtml:

How good is your battery life?
Is your battery absolutely perfect?
Did you ever want to benchmark your battery life?

If anything happens to the device or to anyone we will not be responsible. Even though the chances are unlikely but a defective manufacturing or any kind of fault may lead to an explosion.
